snippet.title: Fluid SE Trailer (iOS/Android/WP8)
snippet.description: Fluid SE is a thrilling time-trial racer mixed with the arcade gameplay of Pac-Man, brought to you by Radiangames, creator of Inferno+, JoyJoy, Super Crossfire, and more.  Fluid SE will be available on iOS, Android, and WP8 for $1.99 on June 12th, 2014.
